## sven: a vanguard emulation tool 

as of 15/07, this project has ceased further development due to updated vanguard-api protocols.

this is a (previously functional) poC on emulating vanguards outbound requests api to spoof redundant calls to the anticheats api.

it emulates as the server, sends inbound/outbound request (hwid, info, flags) disguising as vanguard
